result.formatted_address: 4A Soares Ave, Ho Man Tin, Hong Kong
result.name: Top Blade Steak Lab

reviews.text: Great burger, great steak, great dessert and delicious unlimited fries. Very good!

Overpriced, bland, tasteless steak with the burgers being roughly 10% actual meat (which hardly even tastes like legitimate beef and more like ground up, soggy cardboard) with the rest of it consisting of what might as well be the fridge itself with bland vegetables and sauce. The fries, while free and aplenty, were not dissimilar to lightly salted strips of plasticine. However, the environment, service and salad soup combo were enjoyable yet overall is a disappointment.

The steak was properly cooked to the level that we asked for. Just one suggestion, perhaps the staff could provide a recommended level of doneness for their steak. Unlimited fries refills is definitely a good catch!

I have been here for two times within short period of time.
For the first time, i ordered the hanger steak, which cost me $268. The quality worth the price.
And for the second time, i tried the flat iron, which suppose to be the signature dish and it really did not disappoint me. The flat iron is even better in terms of the beef taste!
I would surely recommend this to my friend.

Steak is OK, but portion could not be said as a meal. Unlimited supply of fries will help you to get full, but it’s devil.
The famous “Dirty Lemonade” may disappoint you also.
The really bad stuff is that you are always reminded to leave within an hour.
It will be fine if you are rich!

result.adr_address: 香港何文田梭椏道4A號
result.name: Top Blade Steak Lab

reviews.text: 近橫隔膜嘅牛肉👍🏻 西班牙豬扒👍🏻 薯條任食👍🏻 威士忌焦糖凍檸茶👍🏻

特色小店，專做牛扒，選擇相對比較少但食物美味，最好味是慢煮牛(Guest chef's flat iron steak)。 
必須留意每人（包括小孩）必須order 一個主食!
雖然任食薯條，但熱度不夠。
坐位有限，建議先致電訂座，必須齊人才可內進。
Dirty lemon 相對普通但 Dirty lemonade頗有特色!
澳(洲和)牛+Top Blade C Fu=冇得輸

此店專攻扒類，Menu 選擇不多，起初想揀Guest's Chef + Herbly Flat Iron Steak，點知waiter 話兩款好似 (waiter 講左兩次都唔係好明🤦🏻‍♂️)，叫我地揀一款貴D既(USDA...$248果款，詳見資訊👇🏻)......起初真的將信將疑，最後叫左Herbly ... + USDA ...。食完貴果款的確有勝人一籌之處，肉質比Herbly ... 軟熟而且更有肉味😋，個人更喜歡貴款🙈🙈
---
大配角薯條新鮮香脆，不會太油膩(所以會不知不覺食左唔少😈)質素不錯。
二配角Dirty Lemonade 比不同，酸中帶鹹，飲飲下有點似鹹檸lemonade😂，味道都唔錯嫁。
---
小記
一開頭黎USDA ... 時經理邊上菜邊講抱歉，話廚師煎過火，煎到做medium well (落單只左medium)，而且表面有點燶。他主動提出可以換左佢再煎，不過我倆都話唔洗(P. S. 唔想浪費)。所以相中既扒有點燶，食食下係有D 燶味既😢...但欣賞佢地主動認錯👍🏼，我都有信心下次再黎既😁
---
地址⛱
Top Blade Steak Lab (何文田)
何文田梭椏道4A號榮英大厦地舖
---
資訊🖋
*Herbly Flat Iron Steak - $150
*USDA 390 Days Grain Feed Flat Iron - $248
Dirty Lemonade - $45
*with all-you-can-eat fries
